	* src/kahua-spvr.scm:
	  Fixed some bugs and cleaned some code up.

	* src/kahua-spvr.scm:
	  Now the signal mask of "root" thread is restored periodically,
	  in order to avoid that the sigmask is changed unexpectedly on
	  Mac OS X 10.4.  This is a temporary step.

